68
00:05:15,726 --> 00:05:17,964
un yetst bet men nor tsu zayn gezunt,

69
00:05:18,223 --> 00:05:25,288
und un dos bay undz di ibergeblibene zogt men az dos ales bay undz geshenkte yorn.

70
00:05:25,395 --> 00:05:32,766
vi la- vos m'lebt iz vi geshenkt far undz fun got. oyb s'do a got. veys ikh nisht.

71
00:05:32,766 --> 00:05:34,940
mit di tfiln vel ikh dir fartseyln.

72
00:05:35,976 --> 00:05:41,854
ikh hob ikh hob gegloybt, in der heym hob ikh geve- frum, ikh hob gedavnt dray mol a tog.

73
00:05:41,854 --> 00:05:43,449
ven ikh bin gegangen davenen,

74
00:05:43,449 --> 00:05:49,228
un ikh bin tsugekumen tsu di seyfer-toyres azoy vi s'volt geven azoy vi Moyshe Rabeyne gekumen in barg, azoy vi m'tsaygt

75
00:05:49,228 --> 00:05:51,495
in di pelikulas Moyshe gekumen.

76
00:05:51,788 --> 00:05:57,806
un azoy moyredik, s'gekumen yomkiper ikh hob moyre gehat. zeyer yidish geshtumt.

77
00:05:57,964 --> 00:06:00,084
BUT ikh bin gekumen in lager arayn,

78
00:06:00,090 --> 00:06:04,432
ven zey hobn gezogt m'zol opgebn di gold un zilber un ale vert zakhn,

79
00:06:04,432 --> 00:06:08,386
un zey hobn gezukht bay undz dos gelt, hob ikh gehat di tfiln.

80
00:06:08,393 --> 00:06:13,247
iz gekumen der S. ikh denk s'geven a doytsh, oder der ukrainer,

81
00:06:13,270 --> 00:06:19,811
mit zayn bayonet, gegebn a hak iber di tfiln oyf di helft, gezukht gelt, un er hot es gevorfn tsu di bazura.

82
00:06:20,290 --> 00:06:22,393
un s'hot gornisht pasirt tsu im.

83
00:06:22,804 --> 00:06:26,578
un den nokh a zakh, ven m'hot aroysgeshikt di yidn fun Tshmelev,

84
00:06:26,601 --> 00:06:32,450
ven zey hobn ale dos gantse shtetl gegangen tsum ro- rebn, in di in di shul arayn,

85
00:06:32,473 --> 00:06:39,555
m'hot oyfgemakht di Shulkhn Orekh, bay di seyfer-toyres un m'hot ale geveynt, un gebetn tsu got,

86
00:06:40,084 --> 00:06:46,710
