87
00:06:46,767 --> 00:06:53,324
ikh hob di ale zakhn gezen. ikh hob gezen in Aushvits vi m'brent di yidn. un keyner redt gornisht.

88
00:06:55,035 --> 00:07:01,054
bin ikh shoyn fartsveyflt tsi efsher undzer got, tsi er klert fun undz tsi s'do a got.

89
00:07:01,330 --> 00:07:08,245
un ikh gey nokh yede yor gey ikh tsum davenen, rosheshone yomkiper, vayl s'iz in mir.

90
00:07:08,245 --> 00:07:11,921
BECAUSE, nisht BECAUSE ikh gey ikh gloyb nokh azoy in a got,

