vayl di mame hot mikh gelernt azoy un der tate, derfar gey ikh.

92
00:07:15,248 --> 00:07:20,443
ober in mir ikh zol zayn azoy religyez, bin ikh shoyn nisht.

93
00:07:20,652 --> 00:07:25,202
ikh bin nisht dergegn s'zol tsurikkumen tsu mir, vayl ikh hob geglikhn dos lebn.

94
00:07:25,461 --> 00:07:26,875
a MATTER OF FACT,

95
00:07:26,875 --> 00:07:31,423
di gants- ikh zog dos tsu rabeyim oykhet. dem RABBI ikh hob im gezogt,

96
00:07:31,423 --> 00:07:35,110
der RABBI vos ikh hob im gegebn a bisl ekstre esn in Aushvits,

97
00:07:35,110 --> 00:07:37,911
hob i- hot er mikh gefregt tsi ikh davn yedn, ikh hob im gezogt NO.

98
00:07:37,911 --> 00:07:41,435
er hot mir gegebn a siderl ikh zol davenen. ikh hob dos siderl.

99
00:07:41,965 --> 00:07:47,156
un un es ligt in mir dos yidishkeyt az tsvey yor tsurik,

100
00:07:47,331 --> 00:07:52,337
ikh hob a a voynung in di berg dort vu ale yidn forn, in di Ketskils,

101
00:07:52,427 --> 00:07:56,926
dort do a frumer vos farkoyfn di ale yidishe zakhn, tfiln.

102
00:07:57,507 --> 00:08:00,555
bin ikh gegangen ikh hob zikh gekoyft nokh a mol a por tfiln yetst.

103
00:08:02,434 --> 00:08:05,803
ikh davn nisht mit zey yeder tog. ikh greyt zikh tsu.

104
00:08:05,826 --> 00:08:09,330
ikh hob a tales, a tales kotn hob ikh, ikh trog es nisht,

105
00:08:09,572 --> 00:08:14,679
BUT ikh volt gevolt lebn tsurik dos lebn vos ikh hob gelebt in Tshmelev,

106
00:08:14,736 --> 00:08:19,776
es benkt zikh mir nokh dem. ober, dos yetst vil nisht kumen.

107
00:08:20,423 --> 00:08:26,407
vi azoy klert ir hot baaynflust ayer lebn alts vos ir hot ibergelebt?

108
00:08:29,063 --> 00:08:31,065
vos hot gemakht a ayndruk?

109
00:08:31,223 --> 00:08:37,950
der ayndruk iz, az m'klert arayn, m'hot farloyrn di yugnt, m'hot nisht gehat keyn yugnt,

110
00:08:38,142 --> 00:08:41,680
farloyrn, ikh bin tsurikgeforn nokh di krig keyn Tshmelev,

111
00:08:42,039 --> 00:08:49,020
bin ikh ven ikh hob gegangen tsu di polyakn, zi hot mikh arayngelozt, nokh gut zi hot mikh arayngelozt in dem tsimer vu ikh bin geboyrn,

112
00:08:49,853 --> 00:08:57,157
ikh bin geganen tsu di voynunger vu mayn mame hot gevoynt, der tate, mayne onkls, mayne kuzinen.

113
00:08:57,157 --> 00:09:03,448
keyner iz nisht geblibn lebn. di di gebaydes shteyen dort, keyn yid iz nishto,

114
00:09:04,821 --> 00:09:07,025
iz vos far a firn ken dos zayn?

115
00:09:08,213 --> 00:09:10,670
demolts ikh hob nor gezogt kadesh un THAT'S IT.

116
00:09:11,858 --> 00:09:16,897
far vos rekhnt ir zent ir lebn geblibn?

117
00:09:18,422 --> 00:09:20,475
un dos di frume fregn mikh.

118
00:09:20,785 --> 00:09:26,803
a nes? ikh veys nisht, ikh veys nisht far vos. a mazl zakh. ikh veys nisht.

119
00:09:27,750 --> 00:09:28,880
ven hot ir,

120
00:09:27,771 --> 00:09:31,055
ikh ken nisht entfern dos. BUT gey, ikh veys nisht far vos ikh bin lebn geblibn.

121
00:09:31,348 --> 00:09:37,485
