122
00:09:38,419 --> 00:09:42,581
ven hot ir zikh getrofn tsum ershtn mol mit ayer bruder?

123
00:09:43,195 --> 00:09:47,475
in ven ikh hob zikh ongezamlt a bisl gelt in Nyu York,

124
00:09:47,481 --> 00:09:50,175
di ershte zakh zog ikh lomikh zen mayn bruder.

125
00:09:50,248 --> 00:09:55,439
un dos hot gemuzt zayn yor nayntsn akht un fuftsik bin ikh aher gekumen oyf Boynes Ayres.

126
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:57,020
dos ershte mol hot men zikh getrofn.

127
00:09:56,408 --> 00:09:57,590
dermont mir,

128
00:09:57,032 --> 00:10:00,249
ye geshribn hot men zikh ye.

129
00:10:00,205 --> 00:10:02,949
dermont mir ayer bruder's nomen.

130
00:10:03,850 --> 00:10:07,911
Hershl in der heym hot men im gerufn Hasha.

131
00:10:09,098 --> 00:10:12,467
Sherman, Hasha. undz rufn nokh Hasha haynt oykhet.

132
00:10:12,793 --> 00:10:18,053
