134
00:10:23,678 --> 00:10:32,919
ir ir vilt epes zogn farn farn di kumendike doyres, far emetser vos zol hern ayere verter?

135
00:10:36,030 --> 00:10:39,130
koydem koydem vil ikh zogn azoy.

136
00:10:41,093 --> 00:10:44,917
az s'zol nisht mer forkumen dos.

137
00:10:45,885 --> 00:10:49,524
koydem vil ikh zogn azoy, a has zol mir hobn geblibn in mir

138
00:10:49,530 --> 00:10:56,004
gegn andere natsyonen LIKE vi vi polyakn, gegn ale,

139
00:10:56,078 --> 00:11:01,185
oder gegn ale doytshn, oder gegn ale ukrainer, trog ikh nisht, nisht gegn ale.

140
00:11:01,191 --> 00:11:07,445
afiles in yetstike tsayt, az ikh ken helfn a a a polyak helf ikh im.

141
00:11:07,738 --> 00:11:14,603
ober oyb eyner ver ikh gevoyer iz a antisemit, er hast a yid, di glaykh ikh nit. ikh hof

142
00:11:14,603 --> 00:11:19,055
ikh hof az zey ebn zikh fun di HISTORY lernen, di ale antisemitn,

143
00:11:19,078 --> 00:11:23,226
az zey tuen gornisht oyf mit dem antisemitishkeyt,

144
00:11:23,226 --> 00:11:30,913
az zey hobn getun a zakh azo kleyn vi m'zogt, vos s'iz meglekh tsu bashraybn.

145
00:11:30,913 --> 00:11:38,119
aza mayn HISTORY vos ikh hob do gegebn, iz hob ikh nisht enk gegebn ales, ven ikh gib enk ales,

146
00:11:38,119 --> 00:11:43,052
volt ets nisht gekent zikh tsuhern tsu dem, un ikh volt nisht gekent redn, ikh volt zikh tseveynt zeyer a sakh.

147
00:11:43,159 --> 00:11:45,009
hob ikh a sakh tsurikgehaltn.

148
00:11:45,083 --> 00:11:51,624
un ven m'shraybt bikher derfun, ven m'shraybt den on yeder eyner fun undz vos zey hobn getun,

149
00:11:52,305 --> 00:11:58,301
volt mentshn nisht gegloybt. oyb eyner volt gegloybt, volt er es nisht gekent leyenen derfun.

150
00:11:58,301 --> 00:12:03,504
azoy shlekht tsen mol erger vos er hot gezen Shindler's List.

151
00:12:03,848 --> 00:12:06,947
un vos er do, vos undz fartseyl'mir di mayses

152
00:12:07,020 --> 00:12:12,684
iz geven toyznt mol arger vos zey hobn getun tsu di yidn, tsu dem yidishn folk.

153
00:12:12,724 --> 00:12:16,206
un a danke got s'geblibn a bisl yidn lebn.

154
00:12:16,206 --> 00:12:21,864
un un un dos vos ikh hob gevolt nor blaybn lebn, ikh veys nisht far vos, efsher iz es a got's zakh,

155
00:12:21,938 --> 00:12:27,450
ikh zol kenen fartseyln di mayses tsu di velt vos zey hobn getun.

156
00:12:27,895 --> 00:12:32,760
ikh bin geven in Aushvits hob ikh nor gebetn ikh zol kenen tsaygn vos zey hobn getun mit a NUMBERS,

157
00:12:32,760 --> 00:12:37,147
un vi zey hobn undz bahandlt, vos zey hobn getun tsu di yidishn folk,

158
00:12:37,147 --> 00:12:40,460
un ikh hof un ikh gloyb az zey zen, zey ebn aynzen,

159
00:12:40,500 --> 00:12:45,523
az s'iz geven a groyse groyse CRIME un s- un s'zol zikh nisht iberkhazern mer.

160
00:12:45,681 --> 00:12:47,919
nisht bloyz far di yidn, far keynem nisht.

161
00:12:49,022 --> 00:12:51,108
d- dos iz ales vos ken ikh zogn.

162
00:12:50,743 --> 00:12:55,344
ir vilt nokh epes tsugebn fun dem vos ikh hob aykh nisht gefregt?

163
00:12:58,708 --> 00:13:05,249
ikh vel enk zogn, ven ikh bin geforn keyn Tshmelev, keygn zogn nokh mer zakhn,

164
00:13:05,323 --> 00:13:10,447
hob ikh gezogt, ikh vel aheymforn keyn Tshmelev, ikh vel nemen bilder ven m'hot undz aroysgeyogt.

165
00:13:11,230 --> 00:13:15,088
hob ikh geven, ikh bin un yetst oykhet, a pinktlekher.

166
